{"tid":1503926,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要求醫管局福利與警務署睇齊","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:38:58.000Z","uid":134993,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e96e0bae4fb670b261845765b800e0e0b4602c7","tid":1503926,"uid":134993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"眼見近月政府施政失敗，導致警民關係惡劣， 一眾醫護人員深表遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n鑒於現時情況及警務處處理前線警務人員的支持手法，我們應為極有參考價值。望醫管局可參考並實施相同政策，以鼓勵一路以來處於水深火熱，默默為香港市民付出的醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n1: 超時工作有補水, 十萬一個月不是夢<br />\n2: 準許員工工作時不帶職員証， 以除後顧之憂  <br />\n3: 高層全力支持前線員工，不道歉不認錯<br />\n4: 接受員工做法不完美但可接受<br />\n5: 如員工受任何工作間暴力，可落閘關門暫停服務<br />\n6: 不論大小醫療事故，堅拒成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n7. 用7.5%人工就可租宿舍住<br />\n8. 過期物品 Expiry date 可以擦左佢，照用"},{"pid":"6a0ff769657b3fd0c811b09fb34daddb2a28042f","tid":1503926,"uid":136967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"push 利申醫護"},{"pid":"adfe49c8dd792acb9db2b3e022cf0e001a8a506b","tid":1503926,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:33:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">全部1點，唯一底線，唔衝禁區(會變恐襲)</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ebb862ee319a73cf3efb03d8626b9a51ae79fe","tid":1503926,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:34:02.000Z","msg"